title: Grateful Dead Live at Onondaga County War Memorial on 1981-05-17
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway->
Promised Land,
Peggy-O->
Mama Tried->
Mexicali Blues,
They Love Each Other->
Minglewood Blues,
Candyman->
Looks Like Rain,
Big Railroad Blues->
Little Red Rooster,
China Cat Sunflower->
I Know You Rider

Set 2

Cold Rain & Snow->
Samson & Delilah,
Ship of Fools,
Estimated Prophet->
He's Gone->
The Other One->
Drums->
Saint Of Circumstance->
Wharf Rat->
Sugar Magnolia,

E: Satisfaction
